sources.description:
Thrill Girls of the Highway! I killed a cop... So what?
Paula Parkins is the teenage daughter of wealthy parents who can't seem to make time for her, so she looks for thrills as the leader of her all girl-gang who harass young men.

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/qSgvW7jD6mE
